OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782202689
OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,FBrexit was branded a "travesty" by
OL,7,Fdemonstrators who marked the 10th
OL,8,Fanniversary of the UK's exit vote with
OL,9,Fa march calling to rejoin the bloc.
OL,11,FPolice on the ground estimated that
OL,12,Faround 1,500 people set off from
OL,13,Fcentral London's Temple station on
OL,14,FSaturday to Parliament Square in
OL,15,FWhitehall behind a banner which
OL,16,Fdeclared "We Want Our Star Back".
OL,26,@nD@VOUnD@_O]xD@JOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
