FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782202689
OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,FThe National Rejoin March (NRM) was
OL,7,Ffilled with people carrying EU flags
OL,8,Fand wearing blue and yellow hats and T-
OL,9,Fshirts that said "Citizen of Europe"
OL,10,Fand "Re:Union".
OL,12,FThe UK voted to leave the European
OL,13,FUnion in a referendum in June 2016,
OL,14,Fcalled by then-prime minister David
OL,15,FCameron.
OL,17,FNewlywed Madeleine Kay, 32, is trying
OL,18,Fto move from Sheffield to be with her
OL,19,Fhusband Johann in Germany.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@dO]rD@EOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782202689
OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,FShe said: "I think Brexit was a
OL,7,Ftravesty for the United Kingdom and it
OL,8,Fhas also had a personal impact of me,
OL,9,Fa huge amount.
OL,11,F"I want to see a better future for
OL,12,Feveryone in the UK, but especially
OL,13,Fthose young people who did not get a
OL,14,Fsay in the referendum.
OL,16,F"It is really important that we make
OL,17,Four cause visible.
OL,19,F"The more that we campaign, the closer
OL,20,Fwe will get to the ultimate goal which
OL,21,Fis being a member of the EU again."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
