PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782202689
OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,FShe said the ramifications of Brexit
OL,7,Fare now being felt in terms of the
OL,8,Feconomy, trade, small businesses, to
OL,9,Frights and freedoms, and "even if it's
OL,10,Fjust trying to go on holiday and
OL,11,Fstanding in that goddamn queue at the
OL,12,Fairport."
OL,14,FThe words "Brexit sucks" was drawn on
OL,15,Fa homemade banner in the shape of a
OL,16,Flollipop while other placard read "I
OL,17,Fdon't want to take my country back, I
OL,18,Fwant to take my country forward" and
OL,19,Falso "Re Join EU for trade and jobs."
OL,26,@qD@ZOUtD@IO]vD@KOUvD@XO]xD@cOUzD@`O]{D@
OL,26,AFOU{D@eO]
