PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782202689
OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,FAnother banner from Croydon for Europe
OL,7,Fsaid "The UK should be more like
OL,8,FCrystal Palace, Champions of Europe."
OL,10,FArttu Rajantie, a Finnish theoretical
OL,11,Fphysicist who lives in Reading,
OL,12,FBerkshire, and works in London, stood
OL,13,Fholding a banner which said
OL,14,F"Scientists for EU".
OL,16,FHe said Brexit had "a big effect" on
OL,17,Fscientific research and saw a loss of
OL,18,Faccess to European funding.
OL,26,@oD@FOUpD@eO]vD@AOUvD@SO]xD@TOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782202689
OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,FProfessor Rajantie added there has
OL,7,Fbeen a loss of freedom of movement
OL,8,Fthat is "really hurting our
OL,9,Frecruitment and building links with
OL,10,Fnew partners in Europe".
OL,12,FHe said: "We can't recruit young
OL,13,FEuropean researchers in the same way
OL,14,Fas we could because they have got 27
OL,15,Fcountries where they can go without
OL,16,Fany barriers whereas to come to
OL,17,FBritain, they have to get a visa.
OL,19,F"There is high cost and high
OL,20,Fbureaucracy.
OL,26,@pD@IOUrD@WO]tD@JOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
