OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782202689
OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,F"It is very complicated and so they
OL,7,Fjust choose to go elsewhere."
OL,9,FNRM organiser Clare Hall said: "I
OL,10,Fwould just like to see full rejoin ` I
OL,11,Fdon't feel like we have got nothing to
OL,12,Flose."
OL,14,FShe said the past decade has shown
OL,15,Fthat Brexit was bad, adding: "It was
OL,16,Fall based on immigration, and that has
OL,17,Fbeen proved to be absolute nonsense,
OL,18,Ffreedom of movement has been stripped
OL,19,Faway."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@]O]qD@`OUtD@FO]wD@^OU{D@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
