OL,3,CBrexit 10 years on: Hundreds march
OL,4,Cthrough capital calling to rejoin EU
OL,6,FShe said "life has got harder,"
OL,7,Fshopping is more expensive, there is
OL,8,Fred tape getting food into the county
OL,9,Fand feels strongly for the younger
OL,10,Fgeneration who are set "to pay the
OL,11,Fprice of this".
